2. The 28th day of February 2023 is appointed as the day on which the 
National Cultural Institutions (National Concert Hall) (Amendment) Act 2023 
(No. 1 of 2023) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

27 February, 2023. 

CATHERINE MARTIN, 

Minister for Tourism, Culture, Arts, Gaeltacht, Sport and 
Media. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 24th March, 2023.
